# Capacity Planning Tools
# These tools are defined inline in the agent DSL files.
# This file serves as a tool registry reference for the v2 export format.

# Tools:
#   get_traffic_analytics — Get traffic analytics and congestion data for a region
#   get_capacity_forecast — Generate 90-day capacity forecast for a region
#   simulate_traffic_shift — Simulate a traffic shift before execution
#   execute_traffic_shift — Execute an approved traffic shift
#   get_subscriber_experience — Get real-time subscriber experience metrics
